  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/3eaa94b503f883312db87a274dd88f54.webp?t=1730192659\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>Discover the secrets of the Hidden Rooms, and what is happening at Monster High™.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/c0a532f5bc85b58fc955fb0ca3df3945.poster.avif?t=1730192659\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/c0a532f5bc85b58fc955fb0ca3df3945.webm?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/c0a532f5bc85b58fc955fb0ca3df3945.mp4?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It’s your first day at Monster High™, where all monsters are welcome… but some strange events are happening.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/f750f319f7743310fff9c2893f6cc363.webp?t=1730192659\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>Be yourself. Be unique. Be a Monster™. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/acaa0aae364ccb9422d681840a9c091f.poster.avif?t=1730192659\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/acaa0aae364ccb9422d681840a9c091f.webm?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/acaa0aae364ccb9422d681840a9c091f.mp4?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Create your unique monster character with a vault full of different monster kinds, skills, and scary-chic looks to choose from. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/e216be85a9808fafa944e4422d4d17e0.webp?t=1730192659\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>Clawdeen, Draculaura, and Frankie are your new beasties!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/49d2cd87475cae8b447e5ed2a38f567a.poster.avif?t=1730192659\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/49d2cd87475cae8b447e5ed2a38f567a.webm?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/49d2cd87475cae8b447e5ed2a38f567a.mp4?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As the newest member of the Boo Crew, you’re in for one hex-citing adventure!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/a5f8ca80352c1977b30411db716156ed.webp?t=1730192659\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>Explore the school with your beasties Clawdeen Wolf ™, Draculaura ™, and Frankie Stein™, and find creeperific clues and powerful new skills. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/1faa5cbb11788ee6c40d1a95a00b46dd.poster.avif?t=1730192659\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/1faa5cbb11788ee6c40d1a95a00b46dd.webm?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/1faa5cbb11788ee6c40d1a95a00b46dd.mp4?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/bc9279a294a0a6bb761bf3624a737468.webp?t=1730192659\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>Unlock incredible skills such as the Vampire Jump or the Gorgon Dash.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/59dadfa37dfe5ef10e00db2651a8028e.poster.avif?t=1730192659\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/59dadfa37dfe5ef10e00db2651a8028e.webm?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/59dadfa37dfe5ef10e00db2651a8028e.mp4?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/06a124b7fa45bcde63b9a7c83b4a0969.webp?t=1730192659\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>Swap Monster Points for new fierce lurks and fashions!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/5affc56580fec60367c0788048e271a4.poster.avif?t=1730192659\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/5affc56580fec60367c0788048e271a4.webm?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322340/extras/5affc56580fec60367c0788048e271a4.mp4?t=1730192659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Can you uncover the mystery of the doors and ancient keys and bring the school back to its authentic, spooky self? Play and discover its skulltimate secrets.<br><br><br><strong>SOLVE THE SKULLTIMATE SECRETS –</strong> Discover the secrets   of the Hidden Rooms, and what is happening at Monster High™.<br><strong>CREATE YOUR CHARACTER –</strong> Be yourself. Be unique. Be a Monster™. <br><strong>MEET YOUR BOO CREW –</strong> Clawdeen, Draculaura, and Frankie are your new beasties!<br><strong>DISCOVER THE WORLD OF Monster High™ –</strong> Explore the school and all its monstrous secrets.<br><strong>UNLOCK NEW SKILLS –</strong> Unlock incredible skills such as the Vampire Jump or the Gorgon Dash.<br><strong>GLOW UP YOUR STYLE –</strong> Swap Monster Points for new fierce lurks and fashions!",
